text: Tripneustes parkinsoni is a species of sea urchins belonging to the family Toxopneustidae.Universal Biological IndexerNatural History MuseumPaleobiology Database These sea urchins have been recorded as fossils on the Miocene of southern France (abt. 20 Ma).Nhm ==References== Category:Toxopneustidae Category:Fossil taxa described in 1846
title: Tripneustes parkinsoni
